    protected abstract static class AbstractResourceService.AbstractBuilder<B extends AbstractResourceService.AbstractBuilder<B>>
extends AbstractGenericService.AbstractGenericBuilder<B,ResourceProvider,ResourceManager>
implements ResourceService.Builder
    An abstract builder for creating resource service instances.

    Builder instances can be reused, it is safe to call build() multiple times to build multiple listener services in series.
